T02TD2190E:64a-1: tsanda badzra kro dha de ba panytsan'a ma mandala bi dhi:/
T02TD2190E:64a-2: bod skad du rdo rje khro bo gtum po lha lnga pa zhes bya ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga / bcom ldan 'das phyag na rdo rje la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2190E:64a-3: gtum po khros pas zhe sdang 'joms //
T02TD2190E:64a-4: stong nyid snying rje dbyer med pa //
T02TD2190E:64a-5: rdo rje 'chang la rab btud nas ;
T02TD2190E:64a-6: / de yi dkyil 'khor cho ga bshad //
T02TD2190E:64a-7: dur khrod la sogs gnas chen du //
T02TD2190E:64a-8: gza' skar dus tshes bzang po la //
T02TD2190E:64a-9: bsnyen pa rdzogs pa'i slob dpon gyis //
T02TD2190E:64a-10: sa brtag pa dang bslang ba dang //
T02TD2190E:64a-11: me tog sngon po lnga dor zhing //
T02TD2190E:64a-12: byin dang ma byin ltas kyang brtag / phan tshun mang nyung autpala kha //
T02TD2190E:64a-13: aom badzra p'ani pushpa p'u dza h'um //
T02TD2190E:64a-14: sngags der bskyar zhing med dang mtshungs //
T02TD2190E:64a-15: btso ma gser mdog rin chen la //
T02TD2190E:64a-16: rngan pa byin la brko bar bya //
T02TD2190E:64a-17: sa sbyang ba dang bsrung bya ste //
T02TD2190E:64a-18: dri yi thig le me tog khar //
T02TD2190E:64a-19: dam tshig lha mo bskyed byas la //
T02TD2190E:64a-20: ye shes lha mo dgug gzhug bstim //
T02TD2190E:64a-21: sa yi cho ga rdzogs byas la //
T02TD2190E:64a-22: de nas lha yi sta gon ni //
T02TD2190E:64a-24: dri yi thig le me tog lnga //
T02TD2190E:64a-25: aom h'um tr'am hr'i: kham dag las //
T02TD2190E:64a-26: dam tshig 'khor lo bskyed byas te //
T02TD2190E:64a-27: ye shes 'khor lo spyan drangs la //
T02TD2190E:64a-28: mchod gtor bstod pas mnyes byas la //
T02TD2190E:64a-29: bdug pa la thogs pu btsugs te //
T02TD2190E:64a-30: dril bu'i sgra sgrogs lnga ldan h'um //
T02TD2190E:64a-31: de nas gsol ba gdab bya ba //
T02TD2190E:64a-32: bcom ldan rdo rje 'dzin pa'i mchog / rig sngags rgyal po dge ba'i mgon //
T02TD2190E:64a-33: gzungs sngags gsang sngags kun gyi gtso //
T02TD2190E:64a-34: gsang ba'i bdag po phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2190E:64a-35: thugs rje'i bdag nyid can rnams kyi //
T02TD2190E:64a-37: slob ma rnams la brtse ba dang //
T02TD2190E:64a-38: khyed rnams mnyes par mchod phyir du //
T02TD2190E:64a-39: bcom ldan bdag nyid gus pa la //
T02TD2190E:64a-40: de yi gnang bar mdzad pa'i rigs //
T02TD2190E:64b-0: sangs @64b rgyas 'gro don byas don gsol //
T02TD2190E:64b-1: byang chub sems dang gsang sngags lha //
T02TD2190E:64b-2: 'jig rten skyong dang mthu chen dang //
T02TD2190E:64b-3: yang dag rdo rje'i spyan mnga' ba'i //
T02TD2190E:64b-4: sems can bstan la dga' rnams la //
T02TD2190E:64b-5: bdag ming 'di zhes bya ba yis //
T02TD2190E:64b-6: rdo rje gtum po'i dkyil 'khor ni //
T02TD2190E:64b-7: yo byad ci 'byor bas bri na //
T02TD2190E:64b-8: deng bdag slob mar bcas pa la //
T02TD2190E:64b-9: thugs ni brtse bar dgongs nas su //
T02TD2190E:64b-10: tshogs pa thams cad dkyil 'khor du //
T02TD2190E:64b-11: byin gyis brlab pa mdzad du gsol //
T02TD2190E:64b-12: de ltar lan gsum gsol btab nas //
T02TD2190E:64b-13: ra ba dra bas mtshams bcad do //
T02TD2190E:64b-14: h'um nyon cig bgegs dang log 'dren tshogs //
T02TD2190E:64b-15: nga ni bcom ldan gtum po yin //
T02TD2190E:64b-16: nga yi bka' las ma 'da' zhig / nga yi bka' las 'da' byed na //
T02TD2190E:64b-17: rdo rje khro bos mgo 'gems so //
T02TD2190E:64b-19: aom sum bha ni sum bha h'um /
T02TD2190E:64b-21: grihn'a pa ya grihn'a pa ya h'um /
T02TD2190E:64b-23: bha ga b'an badzra p'a ni h'um //
T02TD2190E:64b-24: a'arya te tsar hi na h'um phat //
T02TD2190E:64b-25: de nas bum pa'i sta gon ni //
T02TD2190E:64b-26: gser la sogs pa'i bum pa ni //
T02TD2190E:64b-27: lto ba che la mgrin pa ring //
T02TD2190E:64b-28: skyon la sogs pa dang bral bas //
T02TD2190E:64b-29: las kyi bum pa ma gtogs pa //
T02TD2190E:64b-30: yon tan ldan pas lha grangs bstun //
T02TD2190E:64b-31: nas dang gro dang so ba 'bras //
T02TD2190E:64b-32: til dang lan tshva bu ram dang //
T02TD2190E:64b-33: mar dang sprang rtsi rnam pa lnga //
T02TD2190E:64b-34: gser dngul zangs lcags mu tig dang //
T02TD2190E:64b-35: by'a ghra sing ha ha sa de ba dang //
T02TD2190E:64b-36: kanda ka ri ni dra sman lnga dang //
T02TD2190E:64b-37: dri chen dri chu dmar zil mdangs //
T02TD2190E:64b-38: mi rta khyi bya glang po'i sha //
T02TD2190E:64b-39: dmar ser 'o ma gzhon nu'i chus //
T02TD2190E:64b-40: phyed mtho tsam du dgang bar bya //
T02TD2190E:64b-41: kha tshar ma nyams ras kyis bcings //
T02TD2190E:64b-42: 'bras bu can gyis kha brgyan te //
T02TD2190E:64b-43: dris bdug mandala khar bzhag la //
T02TD2190E:64b-44: mi dmigs bhr'um bam bdud rtsi yi //
T02TD2190E:64b-45: rgya mtsho'i dbus su ri rab che //
T02TD2190E:64b-46: sprin sgra bsnol bas sna tshogs sgra //
T02TD2190E:64b-47: lte bar bhr'um las gzhal yas khang //
T02TD2190E:64b-48: bam las chu skyes dam tshig bskyed //
T02TD2190E:64b-49: ye shes 'khor lo spyan drangs la //
T02TD2190E:64b-50: phyag rgya bzhi yis gnyis med bstim //
T02TD2190E:64b-51: sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlab //
T02TD2190E:64b-52: spyan la sogs pas dbang bskur ro //
T02TD2190E:64b-53: mchod dang gtor mas bstod byas la //
T02TD2190E:65a-2: de nas slob ma'i sta gon ni //
T02TD2190E:65a-3: rdo rje slob ma khrus byas la //
T02TD2190E:65a-4: slob ma sgo yi drung gnas nas //
T02TD2190E:65a-5: dga' chen khyod bdag ston pa po //
T02TD2190E:65a-6: slob dpon khyod ni dgongs su gsol //
T02TD2190E:65a-7: byang chub chen po'i tshul bstan pa //
T02TD2190E:65a-8: mgon po chen po bdag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2190E:65a-9: dam tshig de ni stsal du gsol //
T02TD2190E:65a-10: byang chub sems ni stsal du gsol //
T02TD2190E:65a-11: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun te //
T02TD2190E:65a-12: dkon mchog gsum ni stsal du gsol //
T02TD2190E:65a-13: thar pa chen po'i grod mchog tu //
T02TD2190E:65a-15: de ltar lan gsum gsol btab nas //
T02TD2190E:65a-16: slob dpon gtso bo'i ting 'dzin zhugs //
T02TD2190E:65a-17: tshigs bcad 'dis ni gsang sngags sbyin //
T02TD2190E:65a-18: bu tshur theg pa chen po yi //
T02TD2190E:65a-19: gsang sngags tshul spyod cho ga ni //
T02TD2190E:65a-20: khyod la yang dag bstan par bya //
T02TD2190E:65a-21: khyod ni tshul chen snod yin te //
T02TD2190E:65a-22: dus gsum 'byung ba'i sangs rgyas rnams //
T02TD2190E:65a-23: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje dang //
T02TD2190E:65a-24: rdo rje gsang sngags rab bsgoms pas //
T02TD2190E:65a-25: dpa' bos byang chub shing drung du //
T02TD2190E:65a-26: thams cad mkhyen pa tshad med bskyed //
T02TD2190E:65a-27: gsang sngags sbyor ba mnyam med de //
T02TD2190E:65a-28: sh'akya seng ge skyob pa yis //
T02TD2190E:65a-29: bdud sde shin tu mi bzad pa //
T02TD2190E:65a-30: dpung chen dag kyang de yis bcom//
T02TD2190E:65a-33: de bas kun mkhyen thob bya'i phyir //
T02TD2190E:65a-34: bu yis blo gros 'di gyis shig / de nas skyabs 'gro sdig bshags bya //
T02TD2190E:65a-35: bla ma rdo rje slob dpon gyi //
T02TD2190E:65a-36: mnyam nyid thugs la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2190E:65a-37: sprul pa'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2190E:65a-38: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
T02TD2190E:65a-39: sku gsung thugs kyi dor gnas pas //
T02TD2190E:65a-40: gsang ba'i bdag po phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2190E:65a-41: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun gsum //
T02TD2190E:65a-42: byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs rnams la //
T02TD2190E:65a-43: bdag yid dang bas phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2190E:65a-44: bdag gis thog mtha' med pa nas //
T02TD2190E:65a-45: sdig pa bgyis ba ma lus kun //
T02TD2190E:65a-46: bcom ldan phyag na rdo rje yi //
T02TD2190E:65a-47: spyan sngar da ltar mthol zhing bshags //
T02TD2190E:65a-48: bla ma dkon mchog gsum po dang //
T02TD2190E:65a-49: gsang sngags kun bdag rdo rje can //
T02TD2190E:65b-0: dge ba mdzad la @65b rjes yi rang //
T02TD2190E:65b-1: bcom ldan phyag na rdo rje ni //
T02TD2190E:65b-2: dus gsum bde gshegs thams cad kyi //
T02TD2190E:65b-3: gsang sngags bdag por dbang bskur la //
T02TD2190E:65b-4: gsang sngags 'khor lo bskor bar bskul //
T02TD2190E:65b-5: skyon bral mthu ldan khyed rnams la //
T02TD2190E:65b-6: skye rga na 'chi mi mnga' yang //
T02TD2190E:65b-7: 'gro ba'i don du sku sprul la //
T02TD2190E:65b-9: bdag gis dge ba ci bsags kun //
T02TD2190E:65b-10: gcig tu bsdus te bsdoms nas su //
T02TD2190E:65b-11: bla med byang chub thob bya'i phyir //
T02TD2190E:65b-12: sems can kun gyi don du bsngo //
T02TD2190E:65b-13: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed pa //
T02TD2190E:65b-14: bla ma rdo rje slob dpon dang //
T02TD2190E:65b-15: bcom ldan phyag na rdo rje nyid //
T02TD2190E:65b-16: sangs rgyas byang chub sems dpa'i mchog / kun nas dang bas dgongs su gso la //
T02TD2190E:65b-17: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba yis //
T02TD2190E:65b-18: dus 'di nas su bzung nas su //
T02TD2190E:65b-19: byang chub snying por gnas kyi bar //
T02TD2190E:65b-20: sems can kun gyi don gyi phyir //
T02TD2190E:65b-21: bla na med pa'i byang chub sems //
T02TD2190E:65b-22: dam pa bdag gis bskyed par bgyi //
T02TD2190E:65b-23: 'gro ba sems can thams cad la //
T02TD2190E:65b-24: pha ma spun dang ming sring sems //
T02TD2190E:65b-25: bu pho bu mo'i sems bskyed de //
T02TD2190E:65b-26: ma bsgral ba rnams bsgral bar bgyi //
T02TD2190E:65b-27: ma grol ba rnams dgrol bar bgyi //
T02TD2190E:65b-28: dbugs ma phyung ba dbugs dbyung bgyi //
T02TD2190E:65b-29: srid pa chags pa zhi la sgrol //
T02TD2190E:65b-30: sbyin pa'i pha rol phyin pa btang //
T02TD2190E:65b-31: tshul khrims pha rol phyin pa bsrung //
T02TD2190E:65b-32: bzod pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa bsgom //
T02TD2190E:65b-33: brtson 'grus pha rol phyin pa spyad //
T02TD2190E:65b-34: bsam gtan pha rol phyin par gnas //
T02TD2190E:65b-35: shes rab pha rol phyin par phyin //
T02TD2190E:65b-36: pha rol phyin pa 'di drug po //
T02TD2190E:65b-37: mthar gyis bslab dang mthar gyis spyod //
T02TD2190E:65b-38: mthar gyis bsgrub la nan tan bya //
T02TD2190E:65b-39: de nas sdom pa dpog bya ba //
T02TD2190E:65b-40: srog chags rnams ni gsad mi bya //
T02TD2190E:65b-41: ma byin pa yang blang mi bya //
T02TD2190E:65b-42: 'dod pa dag ni spyad mi bya //
T02TD2190E:65b-43: btsun pa dag kyang yang mi smra //
T02TD2190E:65b-44: nyes pa kun gyi rtsa ba yin //
T02TD2190E:65b-45: chang ni myos par btung ma yin //
T02TD2190E:65b-46: sems can gdul bya ma gtogs pa //
T02TD2190E:65b-47: bya ba ma yin thams cad spang //
T02TD2190E:65b-48: dam pa nye bar mnyes byas shing //
T02TD2190E:65b-49: rnal 'byor can la bsnyen bkur bya //
T02TD2190E:65b-50: lus kyi las ni rnam gsum dang //
T02TD2190E:65b-51: ngag gi rnam pa bzhi dag dang //
T02TD2190E:66a-2: ci nus pa yis rjes su bsrung //
T02TD2190E:66a-3: sems can don la rgyab phyogs min //
T02TD2190E:66a-4: theg pa dman la dor mi bya //
T02TD2190E:66a-5: 'khor ba dag kyang yong mi spang //
T02TD2190E:66a-6: rtag tu mya ngan 'da' mi chags //
T02TD2190E:66a-7: lha dang lha min gsang ba pa //
T02TD2190E:66a-8: de la brnyas par mi bya zhing //
T02TD2190E:66a-9: phyag rgya bzhon pa mtshon cha dang //
T02TD2190E:66a-10: mtshan ma bgom par mi bya'o //
T02TD2190E:66a-11: bla ma la gus bka' mi 'da' //
T02TD2190E:66a-12: stong nyid snying rje rab bsgom zhing //
T02TD2190E:66a-13: mdor na rtsa ba yan lag gi //
T02TD2190E:66a-14: dam tshig nyin mtshan grangs kyis bsrung //
T02TD2190E:66a-15: de nas bla mas gsungs pa yi //
T02TD2190E:66a-16: sdom pa legs par bsrung par bya //
T02TD2190E:66a-17: tshul khrims zhes bya sogs pa nas //
T02TD2190E:66a-18: dus 'di nas ni bzung nas ni //
T02TD2190E:66a-19: ji srid snying po byang chub bar //
T02TD2190E:66a-20: bdag ni rab tu sngom par bgyid //
T02TD2190E:66a-21: de nas slob ma'i gnas gsum du //
T02TD2190E:66a-22: rdo rje khu tshur dri yi chus //
T02TD2190E:66a-23: thig le nyi zla pad stengs su //
T02TD2190E:66a-24: yi ge gsum gyi sbyor ba las ;
T02TD2190E:66a-25: / sku gsungs thugs kyis byin gyis brlabs / las kyi chu yis gtor zhing bsrung //
T02TD2190E:66a-26: aom badzra au da ka h'um phat /
T02TD2190E:66a-27: mchod pa lnga yis legs mchod de //
T02TD2190E:66a-28: spyi bor me tog spos byin la //
T02TD2190E:66a-29: mar me dri ni snying gar ro //
T02TD2190E:66a-30: dril bu dkrol zhing bshos gtsang mdun //
T02TD2190E:66a-31: de nas tshigs bcad sngags 'dis sbyin //
T02TD2190E:66a-32: dus 'di nas ni bzung nas su //
T02TD2190E:66a-33: 'khor ba'i nyes pas ma gos par //
T02TD2190E:66a-34: mchod pa kun dang ldan pa yi //
T02TD2190E:66a-35: dus kun du ni bde legs shog / aom panytsa ling+ga aa bhi shinyts'a mi //
T02TD2190E:66a-36: de nas so shing sbyin par bya //
T02TD2190E:66a-37: 'o ma can gyi shing dag la //
T02TD2190E:66a-38: sor brgyad dang ni bcu gnyis pa //
T02TD2190E:66a-39: me tog can ni dor bar bya //
T02TD2190E:66a-40: 'jig rten du ni kun mkhyen rnams //
T02TD2190E:66a-41: au dumw'a ra'i me tog bzhin /
T02TD2190E:66a-43: zhes pa la sogs chod bshad bya //
T02TD2190E:66a-44: aom tra ki sti ba hr'i shuddha sarba dharm'a svabh'a ba badzra a'atma ko& ham /
T02TD2190E:66a-45: de nas srung skud sngon po yis //
T02TD2190E:66a-46: mdud pa lnga ldan byin brlabs can //
T02TD2190E:66a-47: dpung pa g-yas g-yon dag tu bcing //
T02TD2190E:66a-48: ku sha stan gding mtshan ma gdag / ngan na phur bu'i sbyin sreg bya //
T02TD2190E:66a-49: bzang na mkha' 'gro'i gtor ma btang //
T02TD2190E:66a-50: de nas thig ni gdab byab //
T02TD2190E:66a-51: ma dang tam gi ting 'dzin gyis /
T02TD2190E:66b-0: bsnyen pa'i dkyil 'khor @66b mkha' la bteg / gzhon nus srad bu bkal ba la //
T02TD2190E:66b-1: kha dog dkar po'i thig gdab ste //
T02TD2190E:66b-2: mdzes pa'i snod du bcug nas kyang //
T02TD2190E:66b-3: las kyis bsang zhing lhar bskyed la //
T02TD2190E:66b-4: ye shes 'khor lo spyan drangs mchod //
T02TD2190E:66b-5: nyis 'gyur tshad la srad bu bstim //
T02TD2190E:66b-6: rang nyid rdor 'dzin lhar sprul nas //
T02TD2190E:66b-7: byin gyis brlab dang bsrung ba'i phyir //
T02TD2190E:66b-8: bde gshegs mchod phyir nam mkhar gdab //
T02TD2190E:66b-9: sgo dbye gsal phyir sa thig gdab //
T02TD2190E:66b-10: tshangs thig gdab ste bgegs bskrad do //
T02TD2190E:66b-12: slob dpon shar bltas slob ma nub //
T02TD2190E:66b-13: dza gsum brjod la lag tu gtad ;
T02TD2190E:66b-14: / dang po nub ste de nas ni //
T02TD2190E:66b-15: lho byang gdab ste de nas shar //
T02TD2190E:66b-16: nub byang lho nas mtshams bzhir thig //
T02TD2190E:66b-17: rim pa bzhin du gdab par bya //
T02TD2190E:66b-18: cha bzhi cha brgyad rim bzhin du //
T02TD2190E:66b-19: dbye ba la sogs shes par bya //
T02TD2190E:66b-20: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi mu khyud bcas //
T02TD2190E:66b-22: de dag thams cad shes par gyis //
T02TD2190E:66b-23: sngags 'dis thig ni gdab par bya //
T02TD2190E:66b-25: dmar ser smin ma sma ra khro //
T02TD2190E:66b-26: khams nag gyen brdzes dbu yi skra //
T02TD2190E:66b-27: zla tshes mche dkar ljags glog 'khyug / lto 'gros brgyan cing stag sham can //
T02TD2190E:66b-28: yum dang gnyis med thugs las 'khyud //
T02TD2190E:66b-29: sprul pa gdug pa'i tshogs rnams 'joms //
T02TD2190E:66b-30: bgegs chen bsnol ba'i gdan la bzhugs //
T02TD2190E:66b-31: drag po me dpung dbus na 'phro //
T02TD2190E:66b-32: bcom ldan thugs kyi sprul pa las //
T02TD2190E:66b-33: rigs bzhi gtum po rang nyid do //
T02TD2190E:66b-34: shar du rdo rje gtum po ni //
T02TD2190E:66b-35: bdud las rgyal byed dri za'i gdan //
T02TD2190E:66b-36: zhal gcig phyag gnyis skum dog dkar //
T02TD2190E:66b-37: spyan gsum mche gtsigs zhabs bgrad pa //
T02TD2190E:66b-38: skra brdzes lto 'gro stag gis brgyan //
T02TD2190E:66b-39: g-yas pa rdo rje bsnun pa'i tshul //
T02TD2190E:66b-40: g-yon pa sdigs mdzub rab tu gdengs //
T02TD2190E:66b-41: me dpung 'bar ba'i rnam pa can //
T02TD2190E:66b-42: thugs la rdo rje'i khyung sprul lo //
T02TD2190E:66b-43: lho ru rin chen gtum po ni //
T02TD2190E:66b-44: gzi brjid 'bar ba gshin rje'i gdan //
T02TD2190E:66b-45: zhal gcig phyag gnyis sku mdog ser //
T02TD2190E:66b-46: spyan gsum zhabs bgrad mche ba can //
T02TD2190E:66b-47: skra brdzes lto 'gro stag gis brgyan //
T02TD2190E:67a-2: g-yon pa sdigs mdzub rab tu gdengs //
T02TD2190E:67a-3: me ri 'bar ba'i rnam pa can //

T02TD2190E:67b-0: @67b dkon mchog gsum ni bdag la stsol //
T02TD2190E:67b-1: lus dang longs spyod 'di bzhis la //
T02TD2190E:67b-2: dbang bskur dam pa mdzad du gsol //

T02TD2190E:67b-7: gsang sngags spyod pa'i tshul 'di ni //
T02TD2190E:67b-8: khyod la yang dag bshad par bya //
T02TD2190E:67b-9: tshul chen khyod kyis shes par gyis //
T02TD2190E:67b-10: dkyil 'khor dam par dbang bskur gyis //
T02TD2190E:67b-11: bu yi blo gros brtan par byos //
T02TD2190E:67b-12: de nas yang ni sdig pa bshags //
T02TD2190E:67b-13: rjes su yi rang bskul zhing gsol //
T02TD2190E:67b-14: myang ngan mi 'da' gsol ba gdab //
T02TD2190E:67b-15: byang chub sems bskyed lus phul la //
T02TD2190E:67b-16: sdom pa phog ste gzung du gzhug //
T02TD2190E:67b-17: bslab pa yi ni tshul khrims dang //
T02TD2190E:67b-18: dge ba chos sdud tshul khrims dang //
T02TD2190E:67b-19: sems can don byed tshul khrims gsum //
T02TD2190E:67b-20: de nas bzung ste gzung bar bya //
T02TD2190E:67b-21: rdo rje rigs mchog chen po yi //

T02TD2190E:67b-26: nyin re bzhin ni dus drug tu //

T02TD2190E:67b-35: mchod pa'i las kyang ci nus bya //

T02TD2190E:67b-37: tshigs bcad sngags 'dis dam chu blud //

T02TD2190E:67b-49: tshigs bcad sngags 'di brjod par bya //
T02TD2190E:68a-0: de ring phan chad khyod kyis @68a * //

T02TD2190E:68b-35: tshigs bcad sngags 'dis sbyin par bya //

T02TD2190E:69a-2: / bdag la gdung ba'i don gyi phyir //

T02TD2190E:69a-11: 'gro ba'i don du khyod kyis bskor //

T02TD2190E:69a-14: de nas gsang ba'i dbang bskur ni //
